

<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
      <h2><b>About</b></h2>
      <hr>
      <p>Ruby On Rails developer &  growth engineer. <br>Wide range of experiences to draw from. Fast learner. Passionate about tech. Good sense of humour, enjoy challenges!

      <p>Also certified as a Microsoft engineer and a Xerox engineer in South Africa. Have a wide range of experience to draw from, having been everything from an account executive to a lead developer at a startup. Love traveling, even studying in India and spending time working in South Africa.<p>

     <a href="http://www.neilpatel.co">My Blog</a>
  </div>

  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2><b>Stuff I've Written</b></h2>
    <hr>

    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><b><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></b><h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>

    <% end %>

  </div>

  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2><b>Stuff I've Built</b></h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><b><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></b><h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>

    <% end %>

  </div>
</div>







